<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Welcome to {{appName}}!</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            padding: 20px;
        }
        .header {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0;
        }
        .content {
            background-color: #f8f9fa;
            padding: 30px;
            border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px;
        }
        .button {
            background-color: #28a745;
            color: white;
            padding: 12px 30px;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            display: inline-block;
            margin: 20px 0;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
        .button:hover {
            background-color: #218838;
        }
        .footer {
            margin-top: 30px;
            padding-top: 20px;
            border-top: 1px solid #dee2e6;
            font-size: 14px;
            color: #6c757d;
        }
        .features {
            background-color: #e8f5e8;
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 4px;
            margin: 20px 0;
        }
        .feature-list {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
        }
        .feature-list li {
            padding: 8px 0;
            border-bottom: 1px solid #d4edda;
        }
        .feature-list li:before {
            content: "âœ“ ";
            color: #28a745;
            font-weight: bold;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="header">
        <h1>Welcome to {{appName}}!</h1>
        <p>Your account has been successfully verified</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="content">
        <h2>Hello {{name}}!</h2>
        
        <p>Congratulations! Your {{appName}} account has been successfully verified and you can now start using all our services.</p>
        
        <div style="text-align: center;">
            <a href="{{loginUrl}}" class="button">Login</a>
        </div>
        
        <div class="features">
            <h3>What can you do now?</h3>
            <ul class="feature-list">
                <li>Access your account securely</li>
                <li>Manage your banking transactions</li>
                <li>Set up two-factor authentication (recommended)</li>
                <li>Review your transaction history</li>
                <li>Make secure transfers</li>
            </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="footer">
            <h3>Security tips:</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Keep your password secure:</strong> Don't share it with anyone</li>
                <li><strong>Enable 2FA:</strong> Add an extra layer of security to your account</li>
                <li><strong>Always verify the URL:</strong> Make sure you're on the official site</li>
                <li><strong>Log out:</strong> Especially on shared devices</li>
            </ul>
            
            <p>If you have any questions or need help, don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
            
            <p>Thank you for trusting {{appName}}!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br>The {{appName}} team</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>